      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/mujam-al-ahadith-al-mutabara:2:15:5",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/9/2/15/5",
      "text": [
        ": إذا عقل الصلاة قلت: متى تجب الصلاة عليه؟ فقال: إذا كان ابن ست سنين والصيام إذا أطاقه"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "5. [5/104] al-Kafi: Ali b. Ibrahim from his father from Ibn Abi Umayr from Hammad b. Uthman from al-Halabi and Zurara from Abi Abdillah عليه السلام that he was asked about the prayer over a [deceased] child [Salat al-Mayyit] – when is it prayed over him? he said: when he can understand the prayer, I said: when is prayer obligatory on him (to begin praying)? he said: if he is a child of six years, and fasting is when he has the strength for it [is capable]."
        ]
      }
    },
